I did the quest about 12 times long ago that way. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
 <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4796"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Baron Zacatac Soulwanderer</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dabrighter2>Dabrighter2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 115<br> <font color=#333333>(2/4/03 8:15:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1144.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Stein of Mogock faction?</span><hr size=1> Around 20th level or so, I was a poor magician who wanted to get some magic items.  I too tried to do this quest.  I even hired a enchanter to cast an illusion on me.  {I forgot wether it was Dark Elf, or Ogre}  When I tried to do the final turn in, I did not have the necessary faction even with the illusion. {You also don't want to be in Oggruk when you illusion fades}  I researched getting better faction with Ogres.  <br>
<br>
I then created a High Elf enchanter, got him to 12th level {First level to get dark elf illusion} and did the quest.  It was probably faster.  I then did the quest about 5 times.  <br>
<br>
Note, a Dark Elf enchanter could probably do it at an earlier level, but I wanted to keep the enchanter for other reasons as well.  <br>
<br>
Note, on my server, you can buy a Stein of Moggok for 250pp all day, any day in the bazaar.  I have bought them for 100pp.  It is probably easier to get the money than get the faction unless you are a Dark Elf.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.showPrevMessage?topicID=1144.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.showNextMessage?topicID=1144.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1144.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.threadControl?topicID=1144.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1144.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1144.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowerannouncements">Administration<option value="themagicianstowergeneral">General<option value="themagicianstowerfrm32">Class Balance<option value="themagicianst